 p_1(\theta) = \left[\begin{matrix}x_1\\y_1\end{matrix}\right] + r_1\left[\begin{matrix}\cos\theta\\\sin\theta\end{matrix}\right] \qquad\text{and}\qquad p_2(\theta) = \left[\begin{matrix}x_2\\y_2\end{matrix}\right] + r_2\left[\begin{matrix}\cos\theta\\\sin\theta\end{matrix}\right] 
